{"tw": {"2574800": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "暗殺者克羅涅的任務", "steam_appid": 2574800, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/260ca421e600c02ae62801cf0e9da694.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/1b317abcad15f5801fdf904ec3cafcf5.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位父母、手足都被盜賊殺害的少女，來到暗殺公會提出委託。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面對舉目無親，也沒有錢的少女，克羅涅站了出來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「沒有錢，你能付出什麼等價之物?」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「……這個，我的寶物」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少女遞出了自己寶貝的泰迪熊玩偶，而克羅涅收下了玩偶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「契約成立」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >克羅涅帶著玩偶，前往盜賊的據點。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟身為暗殺者的克羅涅，正面對上盜賊能不能安然無恙呢......?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/64fc655231f5d378f42e59cd369c26bf.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按照你喜歡的風格選擇暗殺敵人或是正面對決</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是從潛行到敵人的背後，給他痛快，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還是從正面硬碰硬，都可以減少目擊證人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【只要沒有目擊證人就是暗殺!!】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有特色又有挑戰性的機關</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >經典的箭頭機關，只要踩錯就會讓你無限輪迴!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同時也有獨特的傳送門迷宮，考驗你的記憶力!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隨機的寶箱內容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次打開寶箱都是不一樣的驚喜，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算是同張地圖的