b_paragraph\" >&quot;...This, my treasure.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The girl handed over her precious doll, and Cronie accepted the doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Deal.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crone took the doll and headed to the bandits' stronghold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Crone, the assassin, survive a head-on confrontation with the bandits……?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/64fc655231f5d378f42e59cd369c26bf.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your preferred style.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's sneaking behind their back and ending their miseries,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or going head to head can reduce the number of witnesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【It's assassination as long as there's no witness!!】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique and Challenging Mechanism</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic arrow maze, if you get it wrong, you'll be caught in an endless loop!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a unique portal maze to test your memory!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomized Treasure Chest</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you open a chest, it's a surprise,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if it's the same chest on the same map, the reward is randomized.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have a taste of Gacha-box!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple short story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To match the fast-paced modern lifestyle,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >there's no lengthy plot or complex background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clearing is quick and easy!</p><p class=\"bb_pa