e Assassin Guild to issue a commission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facing the girl who had no one to rely on and no money, Crone stood up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Without money, what equivalent can you give?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;...This, my treasure.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The girl handed over her precious doll, and Cronie accepted the doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Deal.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crone took the doll and headed to the bandits' stronghold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Crone, the assassin, survive a head-on confrontation with the bandits……?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/64fc655231f5d378f42e59cd369c26bf.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your preferred style.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's sneaking behind their back and ending their miseries,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or going head to head can reduce the number of witnesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【It's assassination as long as there's no witness!!】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique and Challenging Mechanism</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic arrow maze, if you get it wrong, you'll be caught in an endless loop!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a unique portal maze to test your memory!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomized Treasure Chest</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you open a chest, it's a surprise,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if it's the same chest on the same map, the reward is randomized.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have a taste of Gacha-box!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple short story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To match the fast-paced modern lifestyle,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >there's no lengthy plot or complex background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clearing is quick and easy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also no need to go for New game++++ just for one missed CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All are unlocked after the first clear!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/a2ba60a38d9552889e550955cd05b694.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/8a0744e5c5c18d9f5ac81a7ebb2bf939.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574800/extras/91cdce6c1f9d2ddff795f70e59993455.avif?t=1762828626\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth exploration RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H scene during battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memory Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue skip</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full-screen mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keys can be changed/Gamepad can be used</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conversation window can be hidden</p></li></ul>", "short_description": "What happens when a proficient assassin enters a thieves stronghold directly? Use skills to backstab enemies from behind, or fight head-on. Will Cronie be able to successfully complete the commission?", "supported_languages": "Japanese, English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese", "header_image":